&lt;span class="c1"&gt;#P hf/cc-pVDZ                    ! Job directives . Hartree Fock single point calc with cc-pVDZ basis sets&lt;/span&gt;
                                 &lt;span class="err"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Empty&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;line&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;...&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;This&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;empty&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;line&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="ow"&gt;is&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;needed&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;job&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;                         &lt;span class="err"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Job&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;descriptor&lt;/span&gt;
                                 &lt;span class="err"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Empty&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;line&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;...&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;This&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;empty&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;line&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="ow"&gt;is&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;needed&lt;/span&gt;
